{"tid":2207651,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"快必遭未審先囚 民主派批部份法官判決不符常理 促改革任命機制","createTime":"2020-09-18T10:02:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-18T10:26:10.000Z","uid":56115,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a43b00b0a0f3ff41cc34f95deb4cb29b2ec0d8c5","tid":2207651,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T10:02:11.000Z","msg":"許智峯指，感到法庭衡量公義的尺度離市民標準越來越遠，令他反思現今司法制度有多大程度能彰顯公義，「如果法官本身冇自覺要制衡行政機關，自然就會成為政治打壓嘅工具」。他認為有必要改革法官任命機制，例如重組司法人員推薦委員會組成，任命應更公開透明，並減少律政司參與，甚至獨立於政府運作。<br />\n<br />\n新民主同盟、荃灣區議員譚凱邦指，警方和律政司選擇性執法和檢控，傷害本港法治，「見唔到法庭有決心扭正呢啲錯誤⋯⋯係冇抗體或者免疫系統去頂住」，淪為司法機器任由政府操弄。<br />\n<br />\n他點名批評東區裁判法院裁判官鄭紀航處理「襲擊長毛案」時，讚揚被控「襲擊致造成身體傷害」的黃森球熱愛社會，只因政見不同，才以金屬利器刺傷梁國雄腰部，准他繼續保釋等候判刑。反觀，案情相近的「襲擊何君堯」案，涉嫌以小刀割傷何君堯胸口的董柏輝卻被控「企圖謀殺」，其他裁判官將被告持續還柙至今。他會考慮正式提出投訴。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200918/HBSFVPTC45BUPDQHNIGVPAFUMQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200918%2FHBSFVPTC45BUPDQHNIGVPAFUMQ%2F&d=U3in%2BbByR8w%2FZmejrHnAdcLrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=9986316e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200918%2FHBSFVPTC45BUPDQHNIGVPAFUMQ%2F&h=a840afdb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200918/HBSFVPTC45BUPDQHNIGVPAFUMQ/</a>"},{"pid":"ddfa3616b4232b2bd9fffb7d876ed2bb8c93c2c6","tid":2207651,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T10:03:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f462184aa77f0563c49e3852ce49bafdf6defb6a","tid":2207651,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T10:03:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37dce21e44f6363c79